<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hospital Management System</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background: #f3f3f3;
    }
    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #38b6ff;
      color: white;
    }
    .topbar img {
      height: 40px;
    }
    .topbar h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .navbar {
      background-color: #04878a;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      color: white;
    }
    .navbar a {
      color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .container {
      display: flex;
    }
    .sidebar {
      width: 250px;
      background: #ddf8fa;
      padding: 15px;
      border-right: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
    .sidebar ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .sidebar li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .sidebar a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      display: block;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .sidebar a:hover {
      background-color: #e6f7ff;
    }
    .main {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .section-image img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }
    .card:hover {
      background-color: #e6f7ff;
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }
    .card a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: block;
    }
    .stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .stat-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: white;
      margin: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .charts {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .chart-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <img src="/public/img/Logo.png" alt="Logo">
    <h1>Hospital Management System</h1>
    <div>
      <a href="#user-profile"><img src="/public/img/icon.png" alt="User Icon" height="30"></a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">แผนกจ่ายยา</a>
    <a href="#">แผนกผู้ป่วยใน</a>
    <a href="#">แผนกผู้ป่วยนอก</a>
    <a href="#">แผนกเวชบ้าน</a>
    <a href="#">แผนกคลัง</a>
    <a href="#">แผนกทะเบียน</a>
    <a href="#">แผนกฉุกเฉิน</a>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="sidebar">
      <h3>Admin Station</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#staff">บุคลากรทางการแพทย์</a></li>
        <li><a href="#patients">ผู้ป่วย</a></li>
        <li><a href="#analytics">Analytics</a></li>
        <li><a href="#reviews">Reviews</a></li>
        <li><a href="#foods">Foods</a></li>
        <li><a href="#food-detail">Food Detail</a></li>
        <li><a href="#calendar">Calendar</a></li>
        <li><a href="#notifications">การแจ้งเตือน</a></li>
        <li><a href="#backup">การสำรองข้อมูล</a></li>
        <li><a href="#report">ออกรายงาน</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    
    <div class="main">
      <div class="section-image">
        <img src="https://www.chiangrai108.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/%E0%B9%82%E0%B8%A3%E0%B8%87%E0%B8%9E%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%9A%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%B1%E0%B8%94%E0%B8%AB%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%A7%E0%B8%A2%E0%B8%9B%E0%B8%A5%E0%B8%B2%E0%B8%81%E0%B8%B1%E0%B9%89%E0%B8%87.jpg" alt="Hospital Building">
      </div> 

      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card"><a href="#register">Register</a></div>
        <div class="card"><a href="#report">Report</a></div>
        <div class="card"><a href="#user">User</a></div>
        <div class="card"><a href="#patient">Patient</a></div>
        <div class="card"><a href="#backup">Backup</a></div>
        <div class="card"><a href="#notification">Notification</a></div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <h2>75</h2>
          <p>Total Orders</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <h2>357</h2>
          <p>Total Delivered</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <h2>65</h2>
          <p>Total Canceled</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <h2>$128</h2>
          <p>Total Revenue</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="charts">
        <div class="chart-box">
          <h3>ผลการรักษา</h3>
          <p>Total Order - 81%</p>
          <p>Customer Growth - 22%</p>
          <p>Total Revenue - 62%</p>
        </div>

        <div class="chart-box">
          <h3>ยอดผู้ป่วยที่เข้าใช้บริการ</h3>
          <p>กราฟแสดงข้อมูลผู้ป่วยรายวัน</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>